text: Dilan Qela (born 7 August 1998) is a Kosovo Albanian professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for Swiss club Neuchâtel Xamax. ==Early life== Qela was born in Neuchâtel, Switzerland from Kosovo Albanian parents. ==International career== ===Switzerland=== ====Under-19==== On 4 October 2016. Qela made his debut with Switzerland U19 in a friendly match against Denmark U19 after coming on as a substitute at 74th minute in place of Mats Hammerich. ===Kosovo=== ====Under-21==== On 30 August 2018.
